{"tid":2498800,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"根本就係巴士站唔夠，大老山先咁塞車","createTime":"2021-04-21T11:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T13:02:17.000Z","uid":25130,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c24a87c5048d2679848811f0ccf9f1279de99f","tid":2498800,"uid":25130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:51:13.000Z","msg":"朝早往九龍方向由小瀝源開始塞，<br />\n夜晚往沙田方向由九龍灣開始塞<br />\n<br />\n問題除左太多車之外，根本就係個巴士站太短，夜晚6 7點，望住左線有成10幾20架巴士連續入巴士站上落客，但果到就得果3架巴士位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果拉長個巴士站是咪就可以令到大老山無咁塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817bd913f01b42a6d6845e5532c36336a7d41c54","tid":2498800,"uid":374427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:51:34.000Z","msg":"連登仔李伯盧開Patreon，需要大家支持！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2498797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2498797</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2f50229f4c121778abd92b9490e7b282de44868b","tid":2498800,"uid":116696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:57:18.000Z","msg":"係香港太多人"},{"pid":"78ac7dbcaaf3acdc72efea84dc6564d9e1094518","tid":2498800,"uid":393495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:14:05.000Z","msg":"往九龍有4個位，早幾個月九巴加咗人指導而家站唔塞，係啲仆街貨車見巴士線完就攝最左收費亭阻住巴士埋去。<br />\n<br />\n往新界就真係唔夠站位喇，得3個，九巴夜晚條友好似唔係好做到嘢，指導唔到"},{"pid":"950979c1c1ef753a8638f0a2c3c503ef36ede558","tid":2498800,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"其實全部強制autotoll 會唔會好d 定龍頭都係klb 個邊"}]}